    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation, though it certainly shows its age. The exterior has several visible scratches, small door dings, and some clear coat oxidation on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin shows significant wear on the seats and carpets, though all essential electronics remain functional. While the car starts and runs, a prospective buyer should expect to address some minor mechanical maintenance in the near future to ensure continued reliability.",
