      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled acquisition opportunity: a vehicle maintained to an exacting standard, reflective of its original showroom delivery. This specimen features flawless coachwork and a pristine interior, having undergone a rigorous multi-point certification to ensure absolute mechanical integrity. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
