      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original deep-gloss luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Step inside to find an interior that still carries the scent of fresh premium leather; the bolsters are firm, the carpets are untouched, and every digital interface functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history that documents its pampered life. From the smooth, responsive acceleration to the silent, refined suspension, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than the best, this is the one.",
